{"id":259,"date":"2025-04-30T00:24:38","date_gmt":"2025-04-30T00:24:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/worldvinguard.com\/?page_id=259"},"modified":"2025-05-05T00:56:44","modified_gmt":"2025-05-05T00:56:44","slug":"privacy-policy-2","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/worldvinguard.com\/privacy-policy-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Privacy Policy"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"259\" class=\"elementor elementor-259\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b06c681 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b06c681\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c4db82 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5c4db82\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Privacy Policy \u2013 WorldVinguard\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7651d73 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7651d73\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"\" data-start=\"161\" data-end=\"337\">At WorldVinguard, we respect your privacy. We only collect necessary information such as your name, email, and order details to process your request and improve our services.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b71aaf3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b71aaf3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Refund Eligibility<\/h5>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bbea48f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bbea48f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"\" data-start=\"407\" data-end=\"491\">We offer refunds <strong data-start=\"424\" data-end=\"449\">within 3 working days<\/strong> from the date of purchase, provided that:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"670\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"542\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"495\" data-end=\"542\">A valid reason is given for the refund request.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"543\" data-end=\"609\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"545\" data-end=\"609\">No report or product has already been delivered to the customer.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"610\" data-end=\"670\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"612\" data-end=\"670\">The service has not been marked as completed or fulfilled.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d25b8bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d25b8bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Non-Refundable Conditions<\/h5>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4cbd59 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a4cbd59\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00a0<\/p><ul><li class=\"\" data-start=\"707\" data-end=\"785\"><p class=\"\" data-start=\"709\" data-end=\"785\"><strong data-start=\"709\" data-end=\"733\">After 3 working days<\/strong>, no refunds will be issued under any circumstances.<\/p><\/li><li class=\"\" data-start=\"786\" data-end=\"904\"><p class=\"\" data-start=\"788\" data-end=\"904\">If the <strong data-start=\"795\" data-end=\"816\">report or service<\/strong> has already been delivered, <strong data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"858\">no refund<\/strong> will be granted, regardless of the timeframe.<\/p><\/li><li class=\"\" data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"1024\"><p class=\"\" data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"1024\">Refunds are not applicable for issues that arise <strong data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"990\">after the report has been sent<\/strong>, even if within the 3-day period.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h4 class=\"\" data-start=\"1026\" data-end=\"1058\"><strong data-start=\"1031\" data-end=\"1058\">How to Request a Refund<\/strong><\/h4><p class=\"\" data-start=\"1059\" data-end=\"1195\">To request a refund within the eligible period, please contact us at info@worldvinguard.com with your order ID and reason for the request.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privacy Policy \u2013 WorldVinguard At WorldVinguard, we respect your privacy. We only collect necessary information such as your name, email, and order details to process your request and improve our services. Refund Eligibility We offer refunds within 3 working days from the date of purchase, provided that: A valid reason is given for the refund [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-259","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/worldvinguard.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/259","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/worldvinguard.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about